(1040, 'I wouldn\'t know how to find eBay on the computer if my life depended on it.', 'Marc Jacobs', 'computers'),
(1041, 'Steve Wozniak and Steve Jobs founded Apple Inc which set the computing world on its ear with the Macintosh in 1984.', 'Kevin Mitnick', 'computers'),
