(2149, 'The problem is when that fun stuff becomes the habit. And I think that\'s what\'s happened in our culture. Fast food has become the everyday meal.', 'Michelle Obama', 'food'),
(2150, 'President Obama is the most successful food stamp president in American history. I would like to be the most successful paycheck president in American history.', 'Newt Gingrich', 'food'),
(2151, 'If we gave up eating beef we would have roughly 20 to 30 times more land for food than we have now.', 'James Lovelock', 'food'),
