(2181, 'We take food for granted but it isn\'t a luxury for many people.', 'Christina Aguilera', 'food'),
(2182, 'If I\'m a lush at anything it\'s food and drink. I\'m not materialistic in any way but I value food.', 'Hugh Jackman', 'food'),
