(2185, 'I love food all types of food. I love Korean food Japanese Italian French. In Australia we don\'t have a distinctive Australian food so we have food from everywhere all around the world. We\'re very multicultural so we grew up with lots of different types o', 'Hugh Jackman', 'food'),
