(2190, 'When I go on Japanese Airlines I really love it because I like Japanese food.', 'Phil Collins', 'food'),
(2191, 'I\'ve been all over the world. I love New York I love Paris San Francisco so many places. But there\'s no place like New Orleans. It\'s got the best food. It\'s got the best music. It\'s got the best people. It\'s got the most fun stuff to do.', 'Harry Connick Jr.', 'food'),
(2192, 'I hate the way they portray us in the media. If you see a black family it says they\'re looting if you see a white family it says they\'re looking for food.', 'Kanye West', 'food'),
