(2196, 'I was eating bad stuff. Lots of sugar and carbs junk food all the time. It makes you very irritated.', 'Avril Lavigne', 'food'),
(2197, 'Well we lost a lot of our independence already. We are dependent on China for credit. We are dependent on Middle Eastern countries for energy supplies. And many Americans are dependent on the government for their income health care education of their chil', 'Jim DeMint', 'food'),
(2198, 'The vast amount of waste and sheer stupidity in government - from the Pentagon to the Food and Drug Administration - could fill committee agendas for years.', 'Tom Coburn', 'food'),
(2199, 'I do not knowingly kill any living thing - including insects or rodents - and I thank my food for sustaining me.', 'Joan Jett', 'food'),
(2200, 'I think one of the terrible things today is that people have this deathly fear of food: fear of eggs say or fear of butter. Most doctors feel that you can have a little bit of everything.', 'Julia Child', 'food'),
