(2204, 'Cats are very independent animals. They\'re very sexy if you want. Dogs are different. They\'re familiar. They\'re obedient. You call a cat you go \'Cat come here.\' He doesn\'t come to you unless you have something in your hand that he thinks might be food. Th', 'Antonio Banderas', 'food'),
(2205, 'Cats have a scam going - you buy the food they eat the food they go away that\'s the deal.', 'Eddie Izzard', 'food'),
