(2388, 'Chronic malnutrition or the lack of proper nutrition over time directly contributes to three times as many child deaths as food scarcity. Yet surprisingly you don\'t really hear about this hidden crisis through the morning news Twitter or headlines of majo', 'Cat Cora', 'food'),
