(4470, 'I need to be cheered up a lot. I think funny people are people who need to be cheered up.', 'Lynda Barry', 'funny'),
(4471, 'Boston is actually the capital of the world. You didn\'t know that? We breed smart-ass quippy funny people. Not that I\'m one of them. I just sorta sneaked in under the radar.', 'John Krasinski', 'funny'),
