(4473, 'I was lucky. My family is wonderful. And it\'s funny because most of my best friends come from very large families. So it always felt as if I had lots of siblings though in the end I had to leave them and go home. I kind of got the best of both worlds as a', 'Sophia Bush', 'funny'),
(4474, 'I think there have always been funny women from Carol Burnett to Joan Rivers. When the audience sees a woman they innately know she\'s worked twice as hard to get there she\'s had to prove that she can be the leader first and then be funny on top of it. She', 'Wendy Liebman', 'funny'),
(4475, 'Justin Timberlake is everything and what more could you want in a person? He\'s funny. He\'s cute. He\'s great. He just understands. I get him and he gets me and that\'s cool.', 'Britney Spears', 'funny'),
(4476, 'When humor can be made to alternate with melancholy one has a success but when the same things are funny and melancholic at the same time it\'s just wonderful.', 'Francois Truffaut', 'funny'),
(4477, 'When human judgment and big data intersect there are some funny things that happen.', 'Nate Silver', 'funny'),
(4478, 'It\'s funny when bands or younger musicians ask me: \'So what does it take to make it?\' Well first explain to me what you mean by \'making it\': Do you want to be a rock star or do you want music to be your livelihood?', 'Eddie Van Halen', 'funny'),
(4479, 'I mean it\'s funny playing music how of course you want it to do well you want them to like it but it\'s not competitive like an election it\'s the Olympics it\'s not a Formula 1 race. The Billboard charts are just to show you what people like.', 'Eddie Van Halen', 'funny'),
(4480, 'It\'s funny how making odd noises can get you into strange situations sometimes.', 'Eric San', 'funny'),
(4481, 'I love things made out of animals. It\'s just so funny to think of someone saying \'I need a letter opener. I guess I\'ll have to kill a deer.', 'David Sedaris', 'funny'),
(4482, 'It\'s funny - if you impersonate somebody they have no idea it\'s them.', 'Tracey Ullman', 'funny'),
(4483, 'Being funny it turns out is like being a bank. It\'s a confidence trick. As long as everyone believes in you you are fine.', 'Evan Davis', 'funny'),
(4484, 'It\'s funny as you live through something you\'re not aware of it.', 'Maya Lin', 'funny'),
(4485, 'Maybe I\'m delusional but I\'m usually funny. It\'s not 100% but I have a pretty good batting average.', 'Adam Carolla', 'funny'),
(4486, 'If Joy Behar or Sherri Shepherd was a dude they\'d be off TV. They\'re not funny enough for dudes. What if Roseanne Barr was a dude? Think we\'d know who she was?', 'Adam Carolla', 'funny'),
