(4488, 'I sometimes lie awake at night trying to think of something funny that Richard Nixon said.', 'Lyn Nofziger', 'funny'),
(4489, 'My father was always a straight-up funny guy. He was silly. He was my inspiration.', 'Mike Myers', 'funny'),
