(4491, 'People ask \'do you make a conscious effort not to swear?\' - if you\'re doing silly stuff you\'re not tempted to put swearing in. All the comics from my childhood who were funny without swearing were the people that influenced me. What I do is quite traditio', 'Tim Vine', 'funny'),
(4492, 'I always find it kind of embarrassing kind of funny and kind of exciting. In New York I\'m recognized a lot although nobody says anything. You know they stare at you just a second too long. But in Paris it\'s not as commonplace to be recognized.', 'Marc Jacobs', 'funny'),
(4493, 'I don\'t think \'Gee I\'d like to dress this person.\' There was a picture in Us magazine. It was a jersey dress and Courtney Love was wearing it. I have this thing about Courtney Love this funny worship.', 'Marc Jacobs', 'funny'),
(4494, 'I grew up in a funny way.', 'Gordon Ramsay', 'funny'),
(4495, 'I got to dress up in funny clothes and run around New Zealand with a bow and arrow for 18 months how bad could that be?', 'Orlando Bloom', 'funny'),
