(4501, 'If you use tact you can say anything then make it funny.', 'Dane Cook', 'funny'),
(4502, 'I think Chris Rock at the Oscars was a great example. I thought that was intellectually hilarious. The Gap starts a war with Banana Republic... That to me was funny.', 'Christopher Meloni', 'funny'),
