(4504, 'You know I\'ve always thought that it would be really funny if somebody made a romantic comedy where absolutely everything went well from beginning to end.', 'Fiona Apple', 'funny'),
(4505, 'I\'m very silly as a person but quality silliness on-screen has more of an art to it. Harrison Ford whom I was in \'Morning Glory\' with has mastered that dry funny better than anyone.', 'Rachel McAdams', 'funny'),
(4506, 'This is going to sound really funny. I have a poster of Zac Efron on my wall! I think every girl has a poster of him in their room so why not join the club!', 'Vanessa Hudgens', 'funny'),
