(4543, 'Nothing\'s funny about someone who\'s successful.', 'Drew Carey', 'funny'),
(4544, 'TV is easier: it\'s all planned out for you and the audience is there to see a show and they are all pumped up but when you are in a comedy club you have to be really funny to win them over.', 'Drew Carey', 'funny'),
(4545, 'It\'s funny because I\'m a sucker for glitz and glitter when it comes to clothes and nail polish but with my makeup I\'m more comfortable with a natural look. It feels more like me.', 'Alison Sweeney', 'funny'),
(4546, 'It\'s funny because it\'s funny.', 'David Spade', 'funny'),
(4547, 'I\'m on so late I\'m definitely the last seconds of anyone\'s attention. So I just want to give them something dumb to laugh at so they go \'That\'s funny\' then fall asleep.', 'Jimmy Fallon', 'funny'),
(4548, 'I recently spent quite a bit of time in Sheffield England which is where I\'m from. I wouldn\'t move back there but it\'s funny when you spend a bit of time in the place where you were brought up. You kind of realize how that place has had quite a big effect', 'Jarvis Cocker', 'funny'),
