(5640, 'I\'ve been asked to do a retrospective since I was about 28 and I always thought that was a bit odd. It\'s great to look forward as an artist because in the future the possibilities are infinite you look back and it\'s all fixed so it\'s a scary thing.', 'Damien Hirst', 'future'),
