(7383, 'I\'m not really big on slapstick humor. I like gentle humor.', 'Anjelica Huston', 'humor'),
(7384, 'If you can understand the humor in the drawing part you\'ll probably get the humor in the audio part.', 'Eric San', 'humor'),
(7385, 'Well the most terrible fear that anybody should have is not war is not a disease not cancer or heart problems or food poisoning - it\'s a man or a woman without a sense of humor.', 'Jonathan Winters', 'humor'),
(7386, 'Kindness and a generous spirit go a long way. And a sense of humor. It\'s like medicine - very healing.', 'Max Irons', 'humor'),
