(7388, 'I am in the Master of Professional Writing program teaching Humor Writing Literary and Dramatic.', 'Shelley Berman', 'humor'),
(7389, 'The man with the real sense of humor is the man who can put himself in the spectator\'s place and laugh at his own misfortune.', 'Bert Williams', 'humor'),
