(7400, 'My family has been amazing and they understand how blessed I am. They\'ve been able to keep my sense of humor.', 'Karen Duffy', 'humor'),
(7401, 'Humor was not important only for me humor was important for this nation for centuries to survive you know.', 'Milos Forman', 'humor'),
