(7404, 'All the people who follow me on Twitter know my sense of humor. I sometimes forget the blogosphere will give it more weight than I intended.', 'Kurt Sutter', 'humor'),
(7405, 'I\'m going to do a lot of weird stuff that\'s not going to be like me prancing around like an insane 12-year-old. I showed everybody that side of me and I think it\'s time to do different stuff even when it comes down to the type of humor. I want to do some ', 'Andy Milonakis', 'humor'),
(7406, 'I have a very dark sense of humor.', 'Andy Dick', 'humor'),
