(7458, 'I think humor is important for all of us and a great comedian is a great treasure.', 'Leila Josefowicz', 'humor'),
(7459, 'Dali had a good sense of humor - obviously you could tell just looking at him he was funny.', 'Joe Grant', 'humor'),
(7460, 'People ask me what the most important thing to take on the race is and I always say it\'s a sense of humor. If you\'ve got nothing but a sense of humor you will survive.', 'Phil Keoghan', 'humor'),
