(7474, 'Comedy is so hard to do so it was very cool to do dead pan humor.', 'Brittany Daniel', 'humor'),
(7475, 'Incongruity they say is one of the main ingredients of humor. Maybe it\'s because everybody can feel superior to me. I honestly don\'t know.', 'Emmett Kelly', 'humor'),
