(7666, 'Clear thinking requires courage rather than intelligence.', 'Thomas Szasz', 'intelligence'),
(7667, 'Skill is successfully walking a tightrope between the twin towers of New York\'s World Trade Center. Intelligence is not trying.', 'Marilyn vos Savant', 'intelligence'),
(7668, 'My dad is still Christian Scientist. My mom\'s not and I\'m not. But I believe in God and that there\'s a higher power and an intelligence that\'s bigger than us and that we can rely on. It\'s not just us thinking we are the ones in control of everything. That', 'Ellen DeGeneres', 'intelligence'),
(7669, 'A government for the people must depend for its success on the intelligence the morality the justice and the interest of the people themselves.', 'Grover Cleveland', 'intelligence'),
