(8081, 'The Bush administration also was not straightforward about the intelligence it had releasing tenuous information that fit its goal of attacking Iraq. I feel deceived.', 'Ken Lucas', 'intelligence'),
(8082, 'Music is an art that expresses the inexpressible. It rises far above what words can mean or the intelligence define. Its domain is the imponderable and impalpable land of the unconscious.', 'Charles Munch', 'intelligence'),
