(8499, 'If knowledge and foresight are too penetrating and deep unify them with ease and sincerity.', 'Xun Zi', 'knowledge'),
(8500, 'The family teaches us about the importance of knowledge education hard work and effort. It teaches us about enjoying ourselves having fun keeping fit and healthy.', 'Kamisese Mara', 'knowledge'),
