(8505, 'Building technical systems involves a lot of hard work and specialized knowledge: languages and protocols coding and debugging testing and refactoring.', 'Jesse James Garrett', 'knowledge'),
(8506, 'When a child comes in I believe that it\'s a \'multipersonhood\' and it knows it its consciousness knows it and it has a nuclei in the center of its consciousness that is the repository of all experience and all knowledge. And when you look in the eyes of yo', 'Shirley MacLaine', 'knowledge'),
(8507, 'After the Berlin Wall came down I visited that city and I will never forget it. The abandoned checkpoints. The sense of excitement about the future. The knowledge that a great continent was coming together. Healing those wounds of our history is the centr', 'David Cameron', 'knowledge'),
