(9334, 'Becoming emancipated at 14 my life wasn\'t normal. I didn\'t have to go to school so I didn\'t. I was rebellious by nature. I spent my 20s focusing on my company Flower Films and producing movies. Now that I\'m almost 30 I would like to try other things in li', 'Drew Barrymore', 'movies'),
