(9345, 'I\'m doing \'Les Miserables\' the movie. I\'ve done a lot of musicals and a lot of movies and I know there are not a lot of people in Hollywood who have been down those two paths so I\'ve been like \'Come on let\'s do a movie/musical.\'', 'Hugh Jackman', 'movies'),
