(10420, 'Honestly I don\'t listen to nobody else\'s music but my own. It\'s kind of like sports to me. You don\'t see Kobe Bryant at a LeBron James game - he just works on his own game. And that\'s what I do. I only listen to me so I can criticize and analyze and all t', 'Lil Wayne', 'music'),
(10421, 'We live in the mind in ideas in fragments. We no longer drink in the wild outer music of the streets - we remember only.', 'Henry Miller', 'music'),
