(10459, 'When music fails to agree to the ear to soothe the ear and the heart and the senses then it has missed the point.', 'Maria Callas', 'music'),
(10460, 'Through literacy you can begin to see the universe. Through music you can reach anybody. Between the two there is you unstoppable.', 'Grace Slick', 'music'),
