(10503, 'You can\'t give up something you really believe in for financial reasons. If you die by the roadside - so be it. But at least you know you\'ve tried. Ten minutes in the music scene was the equal of one hundred years outside of it.', 'Robert Plant', 'music'),
(10504, 'Hip-Hop isn\'t just music it is also a spiritual movement of the blacks! You can\'t just call Hip-Hop a trend!', 'Lauryn Hill', 'music'),
