(10773, 'I\'m obsessed with the countryside: woods forests fields lakes mountains. I\'m really into folk music and folklore. But more so I\'m into electronic music. I\'m into bands that have both aspects like Boards of Canada is a perfect example. You could listen to ', 'Ellie Goulding', 'music'),
