(11183, 'You know I used to listen to music a lot more.', 'Brett Favre', 'music'),
(11184, 'I don\'t care what people say. My music\'s my music.', 'Enrique Iglesias', 'music'),
(11185, 'I don\'t like rap music at all. I don\'t think it\'s music. It\'s just a beat and rapping.', 'Nina Simone', 'music'),
