(11211, 'Look deep into nature and then you will understand everything better.', 'Albert Einstein', 'nature'),
(11212, 'I thank you God for this most amazing day for the leaping greenly spirits of trees and for the blue dream of sky and for everything which is natural which is infinite which is yes.', 'e. e. cummings', 'nature'),
