(12692, 'Making movies is not rocket science. It\'s about relationships and communication and strangers coming together to see if they can get along harmoniously productively and creatively. That\'s a challenge. When it works it\'s fantastic and will lift you up. Whe', 'Julia Roberts', 'science'),
