(13365, 'I do love science fiction but it\'s not really a genre unto itself it always seems to merge with another genre. With the few movies I\'ve done I\'ve ended up playing with genre in some way or another so any genre that\'s made to mix with others is like candy ', 'Rian Johnson', 'science'),
