(13682, 'A supermodel needed to be able to be on \'Sports Illustrated\' to be able to walk runways to be able to do beauty ads to be on covers. And the girls now can no longer be on covers and be in the ads because your actresses have taken over all the jobs. I don\'', 'Kim Alexis', 'sports'),
