(13686, 'We live in a world where sports have the potential to bridge the gap between racism sexism and discrimination. The 2012 Olympic Games was a great start but hopefully what these games taught us is that if women are given an opportunity on an equal playing ', 'Jackie Joyner-Kersee', 'sports'),
(13687, 'I had my boy in Boston on Easter Sunday. That kills me from a sports perspective. He\'s a Boston baby and I\'m a New York guy.', 'Kevin James', 'sports'),
